<style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .product-overview {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .product-image img {
            width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 5px;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .product-details {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        .product-details h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .product-details p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .price-box {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 200px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .price-box .price {
            color: green;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .price-box .shipping-info {
            color: gray;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .price-box button {
            background-color: orange;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .product-info, .additional-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .additional-info img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 5px;
            background-color: white;
        }
    </style>


<%= link_to "Back", "javascript:history.back()", class: "back-button" %>

<div class="container">
    <div class="product-overview">
        <div class="product-image">
            <%=image_tag @product.image%>
        </div>
        <div class="product-details">
            <h1>Leaded Glass</h1>
            <p>Discover our comprehensive range of high-quality X-ray solutions for medical imaging professionals.</p>
            <h2><%= @product.name%></h2>
            <p><%= @product.description%></p>
        </div>
        <div class="price-box">
            <div class="price"> $ <%= @product.price %></div>
            <div class="shipping-info">
                FREE International Returns<br>
                $21.95 Shipping & Import Charges to Mexico Details
            </div>
            <p>Delivery Thursday, September 12 or fastest delivery Monday, September 9. Order within 5 hrs</p>
            <button>Buy Now</button>
            <button>Add to Cart</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-info">
        <h3>Product Information</h3>
        <p><strong>ALSO AVAILABLE:</strong> Hurricane Glass rated for various missile impacts, bullet-resistant glass, fire-rated glass, and both fire-rated and bullet-resistant glass. Call for pricing.</p>
        <p>Standard X-Ray lead glass pricing below is 5/16" thick, providing 1/16" (4 lb) lead equivalent shielding value. Higher shielding ratings are available upon request. X-Ray Safety Glass is available upon request, labeled to meet impact resistance ANSI Z97.1 and CPSC 16 CFR 1201 Cat 2. X-Ray Safety Glass is required in any window that occurs within 25" of any door opening, or within 36" from the floor, per glazing safety codes and regulations. X-Ray lead glass should be utilized in interior applications only.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="additional-info">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x300" alt="Technical Diagram">
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
